venue.address_1: 380 Chief Justice Cushing Highway, Cohasset, MA
venue.name: Whitney And Thayer Woods - parking area near route 3A

item.description:
This lovely park is tucked away on the South Shore. It has beautiful carriage roads, and plenty of side trails full of things to see - including rhododendron, azaleas, and huge stones covered in moss.

I was pleasantly surprised the first time I visited. Below is a link with a full description. Please plan for a 2 hour hike. The pace will be moderate to fast, and led by Kate. Thanks Kate!

Please bring plenty of water and snacks for you and your pets. Please bring bags, and leave no trace.


http://www.thetrustee...
item.how_to_find_us: Kate will be in a blue Jeep Cherokee.
